{"tid":556811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DISCUSS：涉事車長掛住同巴膠傾計　搞到遲到","createTime":"2018-02-10T18:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T02:33:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f08e66dacc35b18c14c6ea0aa01828422e72c89","tid":556811,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T18:34:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27239514&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27239514%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=TUBkqYqUSE21jzqGDr7BtcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=39a5a9c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27239514&amp;extra=page%3D1</a><br />\n巴膠文化害死九巴!<br />\n<br />\n872號九巴係大埔公路翻側，涉事車長係巴迷嚟，出事前掛住同巴膠傾計搞到遲到，仲養部熱狗，今次同佢上次46X咁當巴士係跑車，逢車過車玩漂移，同好多舊巴迷一樣想架車快有推背感，司機位可以開窗勁吹涼風好似熱狗咁<br />\n<br />\n所以巴膠文化害死九巴! 走火入魔，前幾年亂出特見， 策劃部巴迷職員亂畫地圖，請9A巴迷做車長， 依家仲保住個巴迷司機， 得咗啦害死人!"},{"pid":"f4f10760d6ea7d5967c6d7f2d63b1498571798eb","tid":556811,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}